post.description:
Format for json
{"fromAddress":"<email addresses>",
"toAddress":"<email addresses>",
"ccAddress":"<email addresses>",
"bccAddress":<email addresses>,
"subject":"<subject>",
"emailBody":"<email body>",
"attachments":{
"<attachment filename>":"<attachment data>",
"<attachment filename>":"<attachment data>"
}
}

<email adddress> can have multiple email address seperate by comma.
<attachment data> Base64 String encode for file data
